    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/583a9c94a95ce2dcca3053e8517aa332.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/583a9c94a95ce2dcca3053e8517aa332.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组队！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友们一起战斗。与朋友们一起射击坦克。与朋友们一起玩乐。与朋友们共赴黄泉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>最多16位朋友。</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/64a2f1798b6f7a1daf9f21577ada9c18.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/64a2f1798b6f7a1daf9f21577ada9c18.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敌人和Boss</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人……危险又可怕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很多种类！我听说有超过30种。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/07826ee2c53502f1e40e24ad0808bfb4.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/07826ee2c53502f1e40e24ad0808bfb4.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创建、测试和分享</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建你的战役。测试它。分享它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam工作坊？<strong>是的。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/8835be6cfb54544855b0bcf27c8f3948.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/8835be6cfb54544855b0bcf27c8f3948.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >坦克镇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赚取弹珠。消费弹珠。非常放松。为你的坦克装扮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是违法就会遭到警察的射击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/91d5dc30cbc93b549a02919fc2ef8344.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/91d5dc30cbc93b549a02919fc2ef8344.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还有更多……</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >僵尸生存模式、多人足球或团队死斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有很多东西等你去发现。现在就获取吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 加利西亚语, 卢森堡语, 日语, 俄语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 简体中文, 韩语, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
